<section class="primary-content">
  <p>These rides are great as an introduction to club riding due to there short nature and relaxed pace.</p>
  <p>Saturday morning rides depart from the corner of Turner Lane and High Street, <a href="https://goo.gl/maps/ArXDRXnkWEr">Whiston</a> at 9:00am prompt.</p>
  <p>Saturday club rides are much shorter than a Sunday ride, we will be on the road for around 2 and a half hours riding at about 11-12mph.</p>
  <p>Including the café stop we're usually back in the village for around 12:30pm.</p>
  <p>Please take time to read our <strong><a href="<%= asset_path('SitwellCyclingClubSitwellCCGenericRiskAssessment–RoadRides2016.pdf') %>">Risk Assessment</a> on Road Riding</strong>.</p>
  <h2 id="upcoming-rides">Upcoming rides</h2>
  <div id="rides">
    <% if (facebook.length > 0) { %>
      <% for(var i = 0; i < facebook.length; i++) { %>
        <article class="post post--event">
          <h3 class="post__title"><%= facebook[i].title %></h3>
          <time class="post__date"><strong><%= facebook[i].date.day %> <%= facebook[i].date.date %> <%= facebook[i].date.month %> at <%= facebook[i].time %></strong></time>
          <p class="post__summary"><%- facebook[i].description %></p>
        </article>
      <% } %>
    <% } else { %>
      <p>Sorry, we have no planned rides at present. Please check out our <a href="/club-rides/wednesday-evening">Wednesday evening</a> or <a href="/club-rides/sunday-morning">Sunday morning</a> rides.</p>
    <% } %>
  </div>
</section>

<aside class="secondary-content">
  <nav>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/club-rides">Club Rides</a></li>
      <li><a href="/club-rides/wednesday-evening">Wednesday Evening</a></li>
      <li><a href="/club-rides/saturday-morning">Saturday Morning</a></li>
      <li><a href="/club-rides/sunday-morning">Sunday Morning</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>

  <section class="widget widget--sponsors">
    <h3 class="widget__title"><a href="/about/sponsors">Sponsors</a></h3>
    <% include ../../shared/sponsors %>
  </section>  

  <section class="widget widget--instagram">
    <h3 class="widget__title"><a href="https://instagram.com/sitwellcc">Follow us on Instagram</a></h3>
    <div>
      <% for(var i = 0; i < instagram.length; i++) { %>
        <% if (i <= 3) { %>
          <a href='<%= instagram[i].link %>'>
            <picture>
              <img src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" srcset="<%= instagram[i].src %>" alt="<%= instagram[i].caption %>" class="lazyload">
            </picture>
          </a>
        <% } %>
      <% } %>
    </div>
  </section>
</aside>
